         <div>
    <p n="1" corresp="#siksaguru_01.01">As follows I will teach first to the servant of the truth. You will succeed in listening to the discussion of the holy law and the determined state of the holy gnosis. There is what is called the pure circle of three bodily domains, uttered by the teacher to the servant of law. That is probably the action, speech, and mind. If so, there is a feeling of loss in your heart, that is the practice that should be restrained. You should just guard them and fix them, for it is the cause of finding joy and sorrow, and good and bad.</p>
